import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['time'] = pd.to_datetime(data['time'], format='%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['time'])]
    data['hour'] = data['time'].dt.hour
    data['day_of_week'] = pd.Categorical(data['day_of_week'], categories=['Monday','Tuesday','Wednesday','Thursday','Friday','Saturday', 'Sunday'], ordered=True)
    data = data.sort_values('day_of_week')
    sns.lineplot(x='time', y='count', data=data)
    plt.title('What is the overall trend of count over time?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Time')
    plt.ylabel('Count')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['count'] = pd.to_numeric(data['count'])
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='count', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['count'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Mean')
    plt.axvline(data['count'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Median')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of count?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['time'] = pd.to_datetime(data['time'], format='%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['time'])]
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='time', bins=50, color='blue')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45, ha='right')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of time?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Time')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.axvline(data['time'].min(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', label=f'Min: {data["time"].min().strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")}')
    plt.axvline(data['time'].max(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', label=f'Max: {data["time"].max().strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")}')
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
```
